title: Three Days Of Seeing
description:
In this house two years ago, a family of three used to live here. After three days the father went crazy and tied the daughter up behind the house. The family had a dog, and it scratched out her eyes! The parents disappeared... One year went on, and a woman moved in. After three days her eyes got scratched out and she disappeared as well. Then two sisters, Jennifer and Emily, moves in and strange things starts to happend. Day 1, day 2, day 3...

A movie by Sigurd. J. Linaae
